                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-158-off958 t18320405-158-crimeloc960"></join>. On the 20th of February, about five o'clock in the evening, I saw the prisoner go and take a pair of shoes, which hung at the door-post, on a nail; he run away with them about twenty yards - I called Stop thief! and the Policeman took him.</p>
